Photon Driven Rover
LIFI (LIGHT FIDELITY) IS A WIRELESS
COMMUNICATION TECHNOLOGY THAT USES VISIBLE
LIGHT, INFRARED, AND ULTRAVIOLET LIGHT TO
TRANSMIT DATA.
INTRODUCTION
L IN THE ERA OF OVERCROWDED (DATA
COMMUNICATION) WORLD, LI-FI IS A
NEW WAY OF WIRELESS
COMMUNICATION THAT USES LED
LIGHTS TO TRANSMIT DATA WIRELESSLY.
L TRANSMISSION OF DATA IS ONE OF
THE MOST IMPORTANT DAY TO DAY
ACTIVITIES IN THE FAST GROWING
WORLD.
L THIS PROJECT HAS A VERY HIGH
SCOPE IN FIELD WHICH REQUIRE HIGH
SPEED DATA TRANSMISSION.
L POTENTIAL OF LIFI TECHNOLOGY AND
ITS IMPACT ON VARIOUS INDUSTRIES
LIKE AVIATION INDUSTRY,
REVOLUTIONIZING COMMUNICATION,
ENHANCING THE PASSENGER
EXPERIENCE, AND OPTIMIZING
OPERATIONAL EFFICIENCY.

v As light is everywhere and free to use, there is a great
scope for the use and evolution of LiFi technology.
v If this technology becomes mature, each Li-Fi bulb can be
used to transmit wireless data. As the Li-Fi technology
becomes popular, it will lead to a cleaner, greener, safer
communications and have a bright future and environment.
v Street lamps and light of vehicles can be used to access
internet anywhere in footpaths, roads, malls, anywhere
where light source is available.
v The passengers of the airline usually pay a considerable
amount of money for the pay for the dialup speed Wi-Fi on
the plane. Now at the same price as checking a bag, Li-Fi
could easily provide speeds of up to 9.8Mbps when installed
at each seats reading light.

ABSTRACT
Literature review
S.ANOORAG,S.TERESA JENNIFER ,SHASHI CIDDHARTH(2015), this research have
used LI-FI FOR LOCAL NETWORKING AND SMART COMMUNICATION module a
smart way of providing broadband access for home networking and it also reduces
the cost significantly.
Varun Terdal, Jatin Swami, Pratim Shah(2018), this research have used Gesture
Controlled Rovers with Li-Fi Capabilities module uses LEDs at the transmitter and a
photodiode and a speaker to play the audio, we execute transmission of audio
signals , also deals with the aspect of Gesture Control that gives additional mobility
for the transmitters and receivers involved in data transmission.
R. S. VIIKHAS ,SANJANA MUKUNDAN,VARSHA KUMAR , ADINI MUNI VENKATA
SAIRAM(2019), this research have used INTERNET CONTROLLED REMOTE
VEHICLE WITH LIVE RELAY AND LOCAL STORAGE module in which the Internet
Controlled Remote Vehicle is managed and controlled through the web page, where
the user can also access and view the live video relay.
LiFi (Light Fidelity)
technology works by
using visible light,
specifically light emitted
by LED (Light Emitting
Diode) sources, to
transmit data
Working
System Analysis
Our proposed system is a combination of Lifi and Wifi technology to use the
advantages of both the technology.
Light emitted by LED bulbs to transmit data.
Then received by a photodetector which converts them into electrical signals.
CODE IS CONVERTED BACK TO ORIGNAL FORM and after that the machine
works according to the instruction.
Wifi / radio waves can also be used to transmit the data to our car module and
perform the action.
